snippet.title: Best VGM 2318 - Ori and the Blind Forest - Riding the Wind
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1932 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MowlJduEbgY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Xbox One / Switch
Ori and the Blind Forest (2015)
Riding the Wind
Gareth Coker & Rachel Mellis
